The '''''Pran''''' was one of the [[Starship/Legends|starships]] used by the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] to search for the [[Teljkon Vagabond]] in [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]]. After the search for the Vagabond was called off, the ''Pran'' was sent elsewhere.<ref name="Shield of Lies">''[[Shield of Lies]]''</ref>

